Package com.atgenomix.seqslab.piper.plugin.api

Interface OperatorPipelineV3

All Known Subinterfaces:
Collector, Executor, Formatter, Loader, Operator, Partitioner, SupportsAggregation, SupportsAlias, SupportsCopyToLocal, SupportsHadoopDFS, SupportsPartitioning, SupportsReadingDataFrame, SupportsReadingDeltaTable, SupportsRepartitioning, Writer
public interface OperatorPipelineV3
The base contract interface for SeqsLab operator pipeline v3. Note that this is an empty interface. Operator implementations should mix-in at least one of the operator feature interfaces such as SupportsPartitioning and SupportsReadingDataset.
